{"tid":1600464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國會修訂香港人權民主法制裁名單. 加入大公報文匯報記者","createTime":"2019-09-28T15:29:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T15:36:55.000Z","uid":5195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"077a58bc06b6af8300e7b02433ac795402d75882","tid":1600464,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:29:32.000Z","msg":"美國國會雖籠罩一片彈劾總統的氣氛，但參眾兩院的香港熱卻絲毫未減。已獲美國國會參眾兩院外交委員會通過並即將交由大會審議的《香港人權及民主法案》，最新經過修訂的內容針對香港親中共政府的傳媒，並同時尋求拒絕向香港政府出售群眾控制和監察的儀器。法案並且特別點名香港大公報和文匯報。在此同時，美國國會及行政當局中國委員會，在雨傘運動五周年之際，發表聲明支持香港人爭取落實雙普選，又促請港府獨立調查警員的暴力執法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E5%8F%B0/20190928-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B3%95%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%AC%E6%96%87%E5%BD%99%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%258F%25B0%2F20190928-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E8%25A8%2582%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2596%25AE%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%25BD%2599%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585&d=Rk2NG7D%2Bj%2B2oa2j7Wxt8rwX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=8e9cb0c7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E5%8F%B0/20190928-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B3%95%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%AC%E6%96%87%E5%BD%99%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85</a>"},{"pid":"9f585c4086d9df00deaca9eeb6e39ed104be3c3c","tid":1600464,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:32:28.000Z","msg":"正喎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入黎投票呀！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「光 復 香 港」  廢 除 《 聯 合 聲 明 》 第 三 次 公 投<br />